* Change directory to /tmp:
<pre>
cd /tmp
</pre>

* Download libevent-2.1.8:
<pre>
wget https://github.com/libevent/libevent/releases/download/release-2.1.8-stable/libevent-2.1.8-stable.tar.gz
</pre>

* Untar archive:
<pre>
tar zxfv libevent-2.1.8-stable.tar.gz
</pre>

* Change directory name with source codes libevent-2.1.8-stable:
<pre>
mv libevent-2.1.8-stable libevent-nxs
</pre>

* Change tarball name:
<pre>
mv libevent-2.1.8-stable.tar.gz libevent-nxs_2.1.8.orig.tar.gz
</pre>

* Go into ./libevent-nxs:
<pre>
cd libevent-nxs
</pre>

* Untar and place here libevent-2.1.8-stable.debian.tar.gz
* If it's need - change version and comments in debian/changelog

* From libevent-nxs directory execute command:
<pre>
dpkg-buildpackage
</pre>
